full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/7/2023 TO SERVE YOU MORE EFFICIENTLY we are replying to your lettter by handwritten notations. This informal method enables a more prompt response. We trust you will agree that a faster reponse is more important than formality. No record has been made of this correspondence and should you write again concerning the same matter, please return the attached correspondence. May 11, 1992 A72-964-793 asof3-4-9 Terry J. Helbush RE: A28 961 620 Josefa Feliciano 909 Montgomery Street, Ste 303 RAMIREZ-GARCIA San Francisco CA 94133 Mr. Ju discussed the Subject's case with me, whereupon I advised him that as A28 961 620 holds documentation relating only to the Subject, it would be appropriate to file an I-90. I will verify that Josefa Feliciana Ramirez-Garcia, residing at 55 Bepler Street, Apartment 7, Daly City, CA 94014, born in Granada, Nicaragua on November 12, 1906 has been a Lawful Permanent Resident of the United States since November 29, 1989, class AS-6. This is sent as a courtesy -- please submit a G-28 with any further inquiries. Low C happen M-180 (Rev 10-15-75) Y UNITES STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE
